        #classes.site-content
          .row
            .col-12
              .site-content.margin-bottom-small
                h3 Classes
                p For setting up my type features, I put everything in classes. It allows for me to reuse different settings outside the HTML tags. For example, if I want to use an H2 size setting outside the H2 HTML tag, then I can use @extend .h2; or add the .h2 class within my HTML.
